      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00002-000-00053"/>Herrn</addrLine><addrLine>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">XVIII. Spöttelgasse 7</rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="center" type="letterhead"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00002-000-00054"/><hi rend="pre-print"><supplied type="image-description">Fotografie von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10860">Paula Beer-Hofmann</rs> mit den drei <rs type="person" ref="#pmb13923 #pmb2534 #pmb2668" subtype="implied">Kindern</rs></supplied></hi></seg><salute>Lieber Arthur!</salute></opener><p>Ich freue mich:</p><p>I. Daß es Ihnen gut geht –</p><p>II. Daß wir Sie bald sehen werden.</p><closer>Von Herzen Ihr<lb/><signed>Richard</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
